A rare Steve L error that I'll presume was just a typo.

@Petrol RAGS as clued is a pretty common term here. Our neighborhood newspaper is called the West Side Rag. (Although it's now online).

<a href="https://www.westsiderag.com" target="_blank">https://www.westsiderag.com</a>/

